OL,3,CLast minute deal reached to save 180-
OL,4,Cyear-old ferry crossing's short-term
OL,5,Cfuture
OL,7,FA last minute agreement has been
OL,8,Freached to secure the short-term
OL,9,Ffuture of the Fleetwood-Knott End
OL,10,Fferry.
OL,12,FThe service has been running since the
OL,13,F1840s and connects the two towns
OL,14,Feither side of the River Wyre estuary.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
