CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776334011
OL,3,CLast minute deal reached to save 180-
OL,4,Cyear-old ferry crossing's short-term
OL,5,Cfuture
OL,7,FIt was due to have a final crossing
OL,8,Ftoday (Wednesday) - but Wyre Council
OL,9,Fsaid it was "pleased to announce that
OL,10,Fa way forward has been agreed" to
OL,11,Fallow the ferry service to continue
OL,12,F"following constructive discussions
OL,13,Fwith the current operator".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
