PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776334011
OL,3,CLast minute deal reached to save 180-
OL,4,Cyear-old ferry crossing's short-term
OL,5,Cfuture
OL,7,FThe Fleetwood to Knott End Ferry
OL,8,Foperators said following discussions
OL,9,Fwith Wyre Borough Council and
OL,10,FLancashire County Council, it's been
OL,11,Fagreed they'll continue operating the
OL,12,Fservice on an interim basis.
OL,14,FThey went on to say: "Talks have been
OL,15,Fpositive, and discussions are now
OL,16,Funderway towards agreeing a new three
OL,17,Fyear contract."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
